Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:14.88,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}翻譯:小小達ckling  傻瓜三世   校對:傻瓜三世   時軸:雪蘭アニメ   後期:小聖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:42.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}知らない気持ちばかり 覚えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘れかたも教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:04.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}言葉だけじゃなくてさ 震える指の温度から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:11.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}それは誰の希望? 私から溢れ出した願いの雫（DROP）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消えても 消えても 生まれてくるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}答えなき酷い未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:24.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何回目の明日が来るのか わからない夜なら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:28.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}名前を呼ばれたい だって胸が痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}痛くて張り裂けそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:40.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:46.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}私がいつか 空に溶け去る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:53.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強い想いで いまを守りたくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:03:00.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}理由は あなたをもっと見ていたいから…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:42.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  銘刻下我的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}是你  讓我體會到無數不曾知曉的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}告訴我該如何忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:04.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要只是開口  用你顫抖的手指的溫度告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:11.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}又是誰的希望  讓我眼眶中的淚水決堤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即便滑落臉龐  消失無蹤  又會聚滿眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}悲慘的未來裡  我尋覓不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:24.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}長夜漫漫  不知道要第幾次迎來明天時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:28.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}總想聽到你呼喚我的名字  只因揪緊的心口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}撕心裂肺的痛苦  叫我不堪忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:40.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  銘刻下我的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:46.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要等到我  化作天邊星辰的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:53.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強烈的思念  催促我守護眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:03:00.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只因為還想多見到你  哪怕一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:07.43,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The life,it's not for comparing things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:14.40,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}So I hold both of light and shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:22.82,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The rays of stars will bring me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:32.17,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Through the dark nights, I see the way to be shined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:44.55,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I don't know what's right for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:51.89,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}But I know the truth of my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:16:00.36,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The way,if it's all predetermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:07.78,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}And the way I should go all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:16.08,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I swear to go whatever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:23.84,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:36.44,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:07.43,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}生命只有一次  往往沒有最好的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:14.40,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}所以我一手握住光明  一手擁抱黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:22.82,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}天邊星辰的光芒  會帶我來到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:32.17,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}穿過重重黑夜  我踏向那一瞬的絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:44.55,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我不知道  我們的一生該如何奉獻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:51.89,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}但我知道  自己的愛意真摯而無瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:16:00.36,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}這條道路  是我命中注定的坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:07.78,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}這條道路  是我一生必經的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:16.08,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}向天起誓  我將踏上旅途遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:23.84,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我所有過的恩典  將永遠留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:36.44,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我所有過的恩典  將永遠留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:10.16,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Are you going to Scarborough Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:17.46,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:24.72,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Remember me to one who lives there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:32.14,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}He was once a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:42.78,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Tell him to make me a cambric shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:49.91,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:59.33,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Without no seams nor needlework.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:06.59,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Then he'll be a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:42.67,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Tell him to find me an acre of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:50.26,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:57.43,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Between the salt water and the sea strand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:05.57,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Then he'll be a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:14.33,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Are you going to Scarborough Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:10.16,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}您要去斯卡波羅集市嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:17.46,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:24.72,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}代我向那裡的一位先生問好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:32.14,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他曾經是我的愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:42.78,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}叫他替我做件麻布衣衫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:49.91,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:59.33,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}上面不用縫口  也不用針線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:06.59,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他就會是我真正的愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:42.67,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}叫他替我找一塊地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:50.26,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:57.43,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}就在沙灘和大海之間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:05.57,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他就會是我真正的愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:14.33,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}您要去斯卡波羅集市嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:42.12,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}To the point of access you, I'll always be ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:47.59,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}If you go without your joy, I'll chase you with my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:52.05,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Though the window you have been, you've always been in love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:58.68,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}If you go without no tears sad
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:07.52,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Why we're born to this life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:12.29,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}When the dawn is close inside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:17.80,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}we never say good-bye and never see again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:22.25,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}so that mourning I'll live with
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:27.41,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}As ever, been my love, you've ever been the one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:33.00,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I'll love you more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:44.13,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}To avoid a joy that something gives you in your time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:49.69,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}If you lived, if you decided to compromise your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:54.27,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}To the wind blows you have been, I'll always send you love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:22:00.80,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Even if I cannot reach it you at last..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:09.40,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Why we're come to this life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:14.11,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}When we've done it all, Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:19.57,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}we've ever given all each other heart and faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:24.14,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}All the morning we will see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:30.57,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}As ever, be my love, you'll ever be the one forevermore
